The Peoples Democratic Party Political Mandate (PDPPM) will on Sunday 3 July, 2022 hold an extraordinary general meeting on how to secure victory for all PDP candidates across the state in 2023. In a statement by Secretary of the group, Comrade Sunday Edemoye, said the meeting scheduled to hold at Sioberic Hotel, Sioberic Drive, off Ekredjebor Road, Ughelli, Delta State will begin by 1pm. The statement urged members of the group to avail themselves for the meeting, as important issues on how candidates of the PDP will emerge victorious would be discussed. It advised members who will be coming from every part of the state to be punctual in order for them to return early.